# The API reads env from apps/api only — not this file.
#
# Copy these examples and set DATABASE_URL to your PostgreSQL (e.g. Neon):
#   apps/api/.env.example  →  apps/api/.env
#   apps/mobile/.env.example  →  apps/mobile/.env  (EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL, etc.)
#   apps/admin-web/.env.example  →  apps/admin-web/.env.local
#
# Then from apps/api:  npx prisma db push
# Start API:  npm run start:dev
